ğŸŒ Network Design
The buoy network operates using a hybrid communication model:

Primary Channel (nRF24L01) â€“ Long-range transmission to the base station.
Error Detection & Resend Mechanism â€“ If data loss is detected, retransmission is triggered via an alternate route.
